text: Rodrick Kuku (born 6 April 1990) is a DR Congo judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's 66 kg but lost to Wander Mateo in the second round. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Democratic Republic of the Congo male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of the Democratic Republic of the Congo Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics
